{"tid":1691191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（千祈唔好咁做）文宣策略","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T05:46:22.000Z","uid":74586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9b1e66536c2ded2a8bb1534720d2f90486d76e","tid":1691191,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"今日大量green object公然大規模進入私人地方，完全唔理法律，為咗應對呢個問題，我今日瞓晏教嗰時喺夢入面有幾個諗法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span></strong>幫啲狗賣樓，痴佢哋個樣喺侵犯人哋啲私隱，一但轉咗痴佢哋地址同個姓同電話放盤，班green object又點查到喎，同時又分辨唔到邊個真放盤邊個假，班友賣唔出真喺唔得你死<br />\n<br />\n同時又會令到成個樓市大跌，因為太多呢啲放盤啦，點知邊個真姐，咪鬥低價囉，大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好咁做，香港樓市會爆嫁</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3fd9daece2b400ce38e5ab5be0bcd49c882f9e5c","tid":1691191,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bae96b71a1a2f75029debbd0afa385dc4c8ef0d","tid":1691191,"uid":191271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"咩都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【解讀英國】如果你覺得無力，不如入黎睇下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26d9dfab6d63e648154dc8d987e8a5e619f85d57","tid":1691191,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"4830d9202056b077a4d0f2a45c92cfd63450463e","tid":1691191,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"46d399142db071aadd393e61cef1f4acf3ed9fab","tid":1691191,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:37:57.000Z","msg